### Get root 
GET http://localhost:5252/  HTTP/1.1

### Get tasks
GET http://localhost:5252/tasks HTTP/1.1

### Insert task
POST http://localhost:5252/tasks HTTP/1.1

Content-Type: 'application/json'
{
    "title": "Learn Express"
}

### Get task by id
GET http://localhost:5252/tasks/1

### Update post by id
PUT http://localhost:5252/tasks/1
Content-Type: 'application/json'

{
    "title": "Learn Express 5",
    "completed": true
}

### Delete task by id
DELETE http://localhost:5252/tasks/1
